    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, the drivetrain utilizes a mechanical limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut with a recently refreshed suspension geometry, and the double-VANOS system has been serviced to ensure precise variable valve timing. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. A true driver's specification for those who prioritize tactile feedback and high-revving atmospheric performance.",
